menu "SSH client (mqjs ssh.*)"

    config MQJS_SSH
        bool "Enable the SSH client bindings (wolfSSH)"
        default n
        help
            Build the wolfSSH-based SSH client task and expose it to JS
            as ssh.connect / write / resize / close / onData / onClose.
            Adds wolfSSL+wolfSSH to the image (a few hundred KB). Off by
            default; when disabled sshc.h provides no-op inline stubs so
            Stamp builds are unaffected.

endmenu
